description: Calling an early election while struggling in the polls was a gamble for British Prime Minister Rishi Sunak. For some at the top of his ruling Conservative Party, it was also allegedly an opportunity to place a bet of their own.
title: Alleged bets on election date add to woes for ‘incredibly angry’ British PM Rishi Sunak

description: PROVIDENCIALES, Turks and Caicos Islands — An American, arrested in the Turks and Caicos Islands after four rounds of ammunition were found in his luggage, will be spared any prison time, a judge ruled on Friday.
title: American arrested over ammunition in Turks and Caicos avoids prison time

description: British Prime Minister Rishi Sunak said that colleagues who were being investigated over allegedly placing bets on the date of the U.K. general election should “face the full consequences of the law” if inquiries find they acted illegally.
title: Watch: Angry British PM reacts to allegations of illegal betting on election date

description: Eyewitness video provided to an NBC News team in Gaza showed the moments after Israeli tanks and helicopters had targeted a warehouse in the supposed "safe zone" of Al-Mawasi near Rafah.
title: Deadly attack on Gaza's Al-Mawasi 'safe zone' leaves mourning Palestinians wondering where to go

description: Anyone wandering 78 million years ago through the swamplands of modern day Montana may have come across a dinosaur so unusual that scientists have likened it to the god of mischief himself.
title: A giant dinosaur roamed Montana with blade-like horns. It's been named after Norse god Loki.

description: The city of Liuzhou is in one of China’s poorest provinces. But as part of Beijing’s “Made In China 2025” industrial strategy, it is now home to EV car plants for five major automakers, after putting investment and incentives into electric vehicles and by pushing local industry to expand production and infrastructure. CNBC's Eunice Yoon reports from Liuzhou on the city's meteoric rise.
title: City in a poor China province becomes a leading electric vehicle production hub

description: Russian President Vladimir Putin added to the tension in the Korean Peninsula, which he described as "smoldering," by saying Russia would be prepared to supply new weapons to North Korea and warning South Korea from arming Ukraine.
title: Putin does not rule out supplying high-precision weapons to North Korea

description: Video released by the armed forces of the Philippines appears to show Chinese vessels surrounding and slashing a Filipino boat in the South China Sea. This is the latest clash between the two countries in the waterway.
title: Philippines accuses China of slashing naval boat in South China sea
